{"tid":1546264,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"Roy新郎 暴大中擺酒 尤其這新婚 都上了新聞","createTime":"2019-09-06T08:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T09:13:14.000Z","uid":48124,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1246f6bcaef8aa708614dbd04b10bb0553fc01ee","tid":1546264,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:23:21.000Z","msg":"速龍成員 多年前早明言親黃和平<br />\n可恨在是我參警成狂牛 幾年來人格儘現 才無法收手<br />\n<br />\n成婚之前一刻連登裹 難得有人通報才知道<br />\n往日儘放TG永遠做到 怎能預計凍撚水能共我同諧共老<br />\n<br />\nRoy新郎 暴大中擺酒 尤其這新婚 都上了新聞<br />\n不比錢 人人R酒飲 連紅酒都飲 不過我新娘 卻早跟佬走<br />\n<br />\n速龍成員 婚期時竟成為搜尋前茅<br />\n慘淡在是在太子不能尋回<br />\n欺騙我能正義定能回頭 今晚我CU見"},{"pid":"11df136671cd5d4b7a217337bd414b6da3149417","tid":1546264,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:23:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8044921eaa497eacf951d8467b1a77356ce52631","tid":1546264,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:24:03.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c016f1795bdd2e57f071d6535cc3b5b4ac26589","tid":1546264,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:26:21.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 出咗不反對啦！【9月6 反濫捕 抗威權 遮打集會】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543083</a><br />\n<br />\n[重開-置頂]今晩1930 遮打反濫捕抗威權集會 已獲批不反對通知書<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544718</a><br />\n<br